{"tid":687751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"落選港姐新民黨劉聖雪連海報都要抄人","createTime":"2018-06-02T13:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T13:49:21.000Z","uid":16513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9a2a063b72dda9dc45a32646afb470683d4d86bd","tid":687751,"uid":16513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:49:21.000Z","msg":"楊雪盈 Clarisse Yeung<br />\n 1 小時 <br />\n〈鳴謝新民黨落選港姐參考雪盈辦設計〉<br />\n<br />\n蒙煤氣公司支持，雪盈辦事處將於端午節和父親節前周末舉行「有糭大坑」活動，分享節日喜悅。我們相當欣慰，落選港姐、新民黨青年委員會副主席劉聖雪也分享到這份溫暖，將雪盈辦五月四日發佈的設計，強行分享予自己使用。<br />\n<br />\n雪盈辦事處發言人喵喵表示：「我們感謝劉聖雪欣賞我們的設計，並再創作成其粉色版本。不過我們希望劉小姐能尊重知識產權，『參考』我們創作部同工作品前可事前告知及得到批准」；隻喵續指，「我們相當關注本地藝術發展，希望有機會與同業交流切磋。我們誠邀劉小姐和新民黨與我們聯絡，交流創作心得」。<br />\n<br />\n啊，隻喵想順道宣傳，雪盈的「有糭大坑」活動，仍然接受義工和學生報名，立即加入我們吧！<br />\n<br />\n詳情及報名：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/447359142351927/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F447359142351927%2F&d=MByN8l5tr7paOzoQpA3Ku%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=d40f4dad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/447359142351927/</a><br />\n<br />\n#希望佢啲粽料好似佢抄得咁足就好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/34199252_1990033524404650_5278974071931928576_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=0005df9957f49f91cc907b720e2cb44b&amp;oe=5B764494\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F34199252_1990033524404650_5278974071931928576_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3D0005df9957f49f91cc907b720e2cb44b%26oe%3D5B764494&h=6719c91a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/clarisseysy/photos/a.918827314858615.1073741831.901237633284250/1990033521071317/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fclarisseysy%2Fphotos%2Fa.918827314858615.1073741831.901237633284250%2F1990033521071317%2F&d=MByN8l5tr7paOzoQpA3Ku%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=e859a013\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/clarisseysy/photos/a.918827314858615.1073741831.901237633284250/1990033521071317/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}